WEBVTT

00:00:02.750 --> 00:00:06.000
1st: Get hooked

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:09.042
I started spending a lot of time researching it.

00:00:09.125 --> 00:00:10.458
Ugh… I still didn’t get it!

00:00:10.875 --> 00:00:12.875
Oh! The kid holding that bell earlier…

00:00:13.125 --> 00:00:15.125
Could it be those people… maybe?

00:00:15.250 --> 00:00:15.958
Yeah.

00:00:16.333 --> 00:00:17.833
They’re human!

00:00:18.250 --> 00:00:19.750
That’s complicated!

00:00:20.167 --> 00:00:25.250
So all the skeleton enemies used to be human?

00:00:25.667 --> 00:00:27.917
Yeah… that’s complicated.

00:00:28.333 --> 00:00:29.833
I ended up taking them out.

00:00:30.250 --> 00:00:32.375
I couldn’t turn them back.

00:00:32.792 --> 00:00:35.583
And I’m kinda curious about what’s going on behind the scenes too.

00:00:35.917 --> 00:00:37.417
So, yeah.

00:00:37.917 --> 00:00:40.667
By rewatching the story again…

00:00:40.667 --> 00:00:42.208
you get, y-you get even…

00:00:42.333 --> 00:00:44.500
deeper into the story.

00:00:47.625 --> 00:00:50.958
2nd: Can’t resist

00:00:47.625 --> 00:00:49.708
Wait—look, look, look!

00:00:48.958 --> 00:00:50.750
I’m looking, I’m looking! So like—what would you recommend?

00:00:50.958 --> 00:00:52.500
Like, Marvel movies and stuff.

00:00:52.667 --> 00:00:54.667
If you’ve got more, tell me!

00:00:54.750 --> 00:00:55.875
I kinda wanna watch something.

00:00:55.875 --> 00:00:57.750
Recommendations, huh…

00:00:57.958 --> 00:00:59.875
But honestly, at this point…

00:00:59.875 --> 00:01:02.708
isn’t it Doctor Strange? (laughs)

00:01:03.125 --> 00:01:04.542
Yeah, Doctor Strange…

00:01:04.542 --> 00:01:05.417
looks fun.

00:01:05.792 --> 00:01:07.917
Doctor Strange is, like…

00:01:07.917 --> 00:01:10.083
it’s got that magic vibe.

00:01:10.500 --> 00:01:12.458
Yeah—not just regular action…

00:01:12.458 --> 00:01:14.417
it’s got magic stuff too, so it’s pretty…

00:01:14.833 --> 00:01:16.667
I think it really hits for people who like that kind of thing.

00:01:16.667 --> 00:01:18.542
Me, I love fantasy and magic…

00:01:18.542 --> 00:01:19.875
