00:01:20.792 --> 00:01:21.125
Yeah.

00:01:21.125 --> 00:01:22.875
I think Doctor Strange will totally be your thing.

00:01:22.875 --> 00:01:25.167
Oh, then I’ll start with that.

00:01:25.167 --> 00:01:26.250
I’ll give it a try, then.

00:01:26.333 --> 00:01:27.750
Yay! Watch it, watch it!

00:01:27.750 --> 00:01:28.833
I will, I will!

00:01:28.833 --> 00:01:29.875
Yay! I’m so happy—we’ll have more to talk about!

00:01:29.875 --> 00:01:30.917
I’m so happy!

